      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#128168;</span><div class="rc-title">Damp smell from the fireplace</div><div class="rc-desc">Homes near the Yarra valley can get moisture into the flue through winter. Annual cleaning and inspection catches this.</div></div>
      <div class="rc"><span class="rc-icon">&#9888;&#65039;</span><div class="rc-title">Slow draw — fire won't pull well</div><div class="rc-desc">Creosote build-up restricts the flue and makes fires hard to maintain. A clean restores full draw.</div></div>
